      "value": "<p>By 10th level, you have plundered magical knowledge from a wide spectrum of disciplines.</p><p>Choose two spells from any class, including this one. A spell you choose must be of a level you can cast, as shown on the Bard table, or a cantrip.</p><p>The chosen spells count as bard spells for you and are included in the number in the Spells Known column of the Bard table.</p><p>You learn two additional spells from any class at 14th level and again at 18th level.</p>",
